ygData.messageBody:
Yeah...last nite I logged on...no monsters in greater Faydark...i asked ppl
in other zones and
turned out problems are zone specific...so if the one u in has probs...like
the Kelethin lifts had
no buttons...and stuff...try another zone...it worked for me...

Went to Lesser Faydark and yeah!! there were monsters and my pet appeared
when summoned..
only prob was i was getting killed abit too much...they never mentioned
zombies in the guides!!!!

Zanderion(EQ nick) aka Synzzz
